Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Cabugao Primary School in the Municipality of Matanog, Province of Maguindanao, to Datu Cawi A. Lidasan Primary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 776
An Act Changing the Name of the Cabugao Primary School in the Municipality of Matanog, Province of Maguindanao, to Datu Cawi A. Lidasan Primary School
Section 1. The name of the Cabugao Primary School in the Municipality of Matanog, Province of Maguindanao, is changed to Datu Cawi A. Lidasan Primary School.1avvphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
